:: motherWatchTv
/* Mother - Watch TV Together */

<<set $location = "Living Room">>
<<advanceTime 45>>

<<dialog "player">>
"What are you watching?"
<</dialog>>

<<dialog "mother">>
"Oh, just some cooking show. Want to join me?"
<</dialog>>

<<narrative>>
You settle onto the couch beside her. For the next hour, you watch together, occasionally commenting on the recipes and laughing at the host's jokes. It's comfortable, peaceful.
<</narrative>>

<<dialog "mother">>
<<if $characters.mother.stats.friendship < 60>>
"This was nice. We should do this more often."
<<else>>
//She leans against you slightly as the show ends.//

"I love spending time with you like this."
<</if>>
<</dialog>>

<<set $characters.mother.stats.friendship += 4>>
<<set $characters.mother.stats.trust += 2>>
<<if $characters.mother.stats.friendship > 100>><<set $characters.mother.stats.friendship = 100>><</if>>
<<if $characters.mother.stats.trust > 100>><<set $characters.mother.stats.trust = 100>><</if>>

<div class="stat-change">
    <span class="icon icon-handshake icon-14"></span> Friendship +4
    <span class="icon icon-shield icon-14"></span> Trust +2
</div>

<<btn "Continue" "CharacterInteraction">>
